Posts.Content: Jun 20, 2011 03:01PM midnight-dawn wrote: hiya kasi, i was just reading the last words your doctor said..my doctor examined me and in his words " you dont have any of the signs of cancer , i am 99.9prcent certain its nothing "  and didnt even send me fast track, i was that happy i went on holiday to spain.. so was shocked to get a cancer diagnosis after biopsy.. followed by lumpectomy, chemotherapy and radiation... sailed through all treatments none of it was no where near as bad as i thought . 3 years later still smiling ,shame any of us have to go through it, take care .... x
